nitial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">PMTI ekspertlari O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozorida talabning shakllanishi va uning rivojlanish istiqbollarini baholadi.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mehnat bozoriga ilk marotaba kirib kelayotgan yoshlar sonining ortishi, shuningdek, ishga joylashishishi zarur bo&lsquo;lgan kishilar sonining ko&lsquo;pligi sabab taklifning talabdan oshib ketish tendensiyasi kuzatilmoqda. Iqtisodiyotning rivojlanish ko&lsquo;lami ishlash istagida bo&lsquo;lganlarning barchasini ish o&lsquo;rinlari bilan ta&rsquo;minlashi darkor. Bundan tashqari, ayrim kasblar bo&lsquo;yicha mutaxassislarni tayyorlash va mehnat bozorining real ehtiyojlari o&lsquo;rtasida nomutanosiblik mavjud.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Hozirga qadar respublikada iqtisodiyot tarmoqlari bo&lsquo;yicha kadrlarga bo&lsquo;lgan talab o&lsquo;rganilmayapti. Shuning uchun PMTI tarmoqlar bo&lsquo;yicha kadrlarga talab qandayligini sifat jihatidan tahlil qilish maqsadida 2016&ndash;2020 yillarda sohalar bo&lsquo;yicha kadrlarga bo&lsquo;lgan talab dinamikasini baholadilar.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Tahlil natijasida quyidagi asosiy xulosalar olindi:</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- umumta&rsquo;lim maktablari, litseylar va kasb-hunar kollejlari har yili mehnat bozoriga o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">450 ming</strong>, oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlari esa&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">100 ming nafar mutaxassisni</strong> tayyorlaydi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- kasblar bo&lsquo;yicha konsentratsiya koyeffitsiyenti vrach, farmatsevt, &nbsp;tibbiyot hamshirasi, o&lsquo;qituvchi, bank xodimi, turizm sohasi xodimi, shuningdek, quruvchi, muhandis va texnolog kabi kasblar bo&lsquo;yicha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari taqdim etilgan rezyumelarga nisbatan yuqori</strong> ekanligini ko&lsquo;rsatdi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- davlat tashkilotlarida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&lsquo;qituvchilar, vrachlar va tibbiyot xodimlariga</strong> talab yuqori;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- xususiy sektorda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">esa sotuvchilar, dasturchilar, texnologlar va muhandislar, marketologlar va ma&rsquo;muriy xodimlar</strong>ga talab yuqori;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- davlat korxonalari va yirik korxonalar&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ish qidiruvchilardan ko&lsquo;proq oliy ma&rsquo;lumot talab qilmoqda</strong>: davlat muassasalaridagi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining 55% dan ortig&lsquo;i</strong>, yirik korxonalarda esa 60% dan ortig&lsquo;i ish qidirayotganlardan oliy ma&rsquo;lumot talab etadi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- xususiy sektorda esa ish tajribasi asosiy talabdir.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Mehnat bozoridagi vaziyat</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozorini tahlil qilganda, mamlakatda ishchi kuchi taklifi har yili asosan kasb-hunar kollejlari va oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlari bitiruvchilari hisobidan shakllanishini qayd etish mumkin. Umumta&rsquo;lim maktablari, akademik litsey va kasb-hunar kollejlari har yili mehnat bozoriga o&lsquo;rta hisobda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">450 ming</strong>, oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlari&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">100 ming nafar mutaxassis</strong>ni tayyorlab chiqaradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2021-yil oxirida respublika&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">mehnat bozoridagi konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti 2,7 ni tashkil etgan</strong>ini ta&rsquo;kidlash joiz. Bu mehnat bozorida zo&lsquo;riqish darajasi yuqori ekanligi, ya&rsquo;ni ish qidirayotganlar rezyumesi mavjud bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlaridan deyarli 3 baravar ko&lsquo;p ekanligini bildiradi.</h3><table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1140px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-qo&lsquo;shimcha</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mehnat bozoridagi konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti - bandlik xizmatida ro&lsquo;yxatga olingan ishsiz fuqarolar sonining ish beruvchilar tomonidan e&rsquo;lon qilingan bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari soniga nisbati (rezyumelar sonining bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari soniga nisbati).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Koeffitsiyent 1 dan qancha yuqori bo&lsquo;lsa, mehnat bozorida konsentratsiya darajasi shuncha yuqori bo&lsquo;ladi. Agar koeffitsiyent birdan past bo&lsquo;lsa, u holda mehnat bozorida kadrlar yetishmasligi kuzatiladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shunday qilib, mehnat bozoridagi konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti ishchi kuchiga talab va taklif nisbatini tavsiflaydi.</h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">, kasblar bo&lsquo;yicha konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti</strong>ni hisoblash natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, tibbiyot (vrachlar &ndash; 0,02, farmatsevtlar &ndash; 0,18, hamshiralar &ndash; 0,19), ta&rsquo;lim (o&lsquo;qituvchilar - 0,21), bank (0,22), turizm (0,31) va ishlab chiqarish (quruvchilar - 0,43, muhandislar, texnologlar - 0,60) sohalarida mutaxassislar yetishmasligi aniqlandi (1-rasmga qarang).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Mutaxassisliklarning haddan tashqari ko&lsquo;pligi AT (1,31), buxgalteriya (1,55), huquq (1,84) va eng yuqori ko&lsquo;rsatkich iqtisod (4,05) sohalarida kuzatilmoqda.</h3><table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1140px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2-qo&lsquo;shimcha</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Kasb bo&lsquo;yicha konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti mehnat bozoridagi vaziyat qandayligi, ya&rsquo;ni qaysi mutaxassisliklarga talab ortib borayotgani, qaysi mutaxassisliklarga esa pasayganini ko&lsquo;rsatadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shunday qilib, koeffitsiyent bitta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rniga qancha ishsiz (o&lsquo;z rezyumesini bandlik bo&lsquo;yicha davlat yoki xususiy agentlikka topshirganlar) to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri kelishini ko&lsquo;rsatadi.</h3></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); text-align: center;"><img src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(177).png" style="margin-left: 27%;box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 349px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 611px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-rasm. Mehnat bozorida kasblar bo&lsquo;yicha konsentratsiya koeffitsiyenti</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozorini batafsil o&lsquo;rganish jarayonida mavjud bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari va ish qidiruvchilar tomonidan taqdim etilgan rezyumelar haqida ma&rsquo;lumotlar beruvchi ikkita asosiy platformani ajratib ko&lsquo;rsatish mumkin. Bular:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Bandlik va mehnat munosabatlari vazirligining ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasi</strong>;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">nodavlat ma&rsquo;lumot bazalari</strong> (masalan, bugungi kunda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">HeadHunter kompaniyasi va Olx.uz sayti</strong> eng ommabop bazalar hisoblanadi).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Vazirlikning ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">49 959 ta ish beruvchi korxona, 6829 ta rezyume va 980 mingta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni</strong> ro&lsquo;yxatga olingan. HeadHunter kompaniyasining bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasida juda ko&lsquo;p rezyumelar mavjud, ammo shunga qaramay,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari soni ancha kam, atigi 4209 ta, rezyumelar soni &nbsp;248735 ta, kompaniyalar soni 10901 ta.</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bandlik va mehnat munosabatlari vazirligining ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasiga ko&lsquo;ra (2-rasmga qarang) tarmoqlar bo&lsquo;yicha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&lsquo;qituvchilar, shifokorlar, hamshiralar, ta&rsquo;mirlovchilar, farmatsevtlar, texnolog va muhandislar</strong>ga talab juda yuqori. Shuni ta&rsquo;kidlash kerakki, bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarida bugungi kunda dunyoda talab yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan dasturchi, marketolog, menejer va onlayn operator kabi kasblar deyarli ko&lsquo;rsatilmagan.</h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); text-align: center;"><img src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(178).png" style="margin-left: 27%;box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 396px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 625px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1-rasm. Bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari soni bo&lsquo;yicha mutaxassisliklar o&lsquo;ntaligi (umumiy bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari soniga nisbatan foiz hisobida)</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">HeadHunter kompaniyasining bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasida talab yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan kasblar ro&lsquo;yxati vazirlikning bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari bazasidagidan keskin farq qiladi. Masalan, savdo bo&lsquo;yicha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">menejerlar (868 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni), axborot texnologiyasi, internet va telekommunikatsiya sohasi mutaxassislari (522 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni), marketing, reklama va PR bo&lsquo;yicha xodimlar (401 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni), buxgalterlar (390 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni) va ma&rsquo;muriy xodimlar (326 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni)ga talab juda yuqori ekani ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi.</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Olx.uz saytiga</strong> joylashtirilgan bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari ham tahlil qilindi. Ushbu saytning ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasida jami 20 mingga yaqin ish o&lsquo;rni mavjud va 6,4 mingga yaqin rezyume ro&lsquo;yxatga olingan. Eng yuqori talab&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">savdo-sotiq (3085 bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni), barlar, restoranlar (3054 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni), ishlab chiqarish, energetika (2715 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni) va ta&rsquo;lim (1221 ta bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rni)</strong> kabi sohalarga ekanligi aniqlandi. Ishchi kuchi taklifi quyidagi yo&lsquo;nalishlar bo&lsquo;yicha yuqori ekanligi aniqlandi:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">qurilish bo&lsquo;yicha mutaxassislar (1138 nafar), huquq, buxgalteriya hisobi (594 nafar) va ta&rsquo;lim sohasi (568 nafar).</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Malakali kadrlar bilan ta&rsquo;minlanganlik darajasi</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda bandlik siyosatini yuritishda asosiy e&rsquo;tibor daromad 5 ming dollardan kam bo&lsquo;lmagan xorijiy mamlakatlarga qaratiladi.</strong> Chunki O&lsquo;zbekiston iqtisodiyotini rivojlantirishning ustuvor yo&lsquo;nalishi ushbu mamlakatlar darajasiga erishish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bu mamlakatlarda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">yuqori malakali kadrlar bilan ta&rsquo;minlashga katta e&rsquo;tibor qaratiladi</strong>. Xususan, tibbiyot sohasiga alohida e&rsquo;tibor qaratilmoqda.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Yevropa va Amerika mamlakatlarida</strong> har 10 ming kishiga&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">80 nafardan ortiq hamshira to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri kelsa (81 va 83)</strong>, O&lsquo;zbekistonda ushbu ko&lsquo;rsatkich 108 nafarni tashkil etadi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Raqamlar</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">O&lsquo;zbekiston</strong> shifokorlar va hamshiralar bilan ta&rsquo;minlash ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari bo&lsquo;yicha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">rivojlangan mamlakatlardan farq qilmasligidan dalolat beradi</strong>. Shunga qaramay, mamlakatimizda yuqori malakali tibbiyot xodimlari yetishmaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek, bugungi kunda qayta ishlash sanoatining ulushi kamida 20 foizni tashkil etuvchi,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">daromad darajasi o&lsquo;rtachadan yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan</strong> mamlakatlarda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">har 1 million kishiga o&lsquo;rtacha 1500-2000 nafar muhandis va tabiiy fanlar bo&lsquo;yicha mutaxassis to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladi</strong>. O&lsquo;zbekistonda esa ushbu ko&lsquo;rsatkich&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">har 1 million kishiga 532 nafarni tashkil etadi</strong>. Shuning uchun mamlakatimizda sanoat uchun yuqori malakali kadrlar tayyorlash talab etiladi. Har yili ta&rsquo;lim muassasalari kamida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20 ming nafar yuqori malakali muhandis va ishlab chiqarish texnologlarini tayyorlashi zarur</strong>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Xorijiy davlatlar va O&lsquo;zbekiston o&lsquo;rtasidagi taqqoslash tahlili shuni ko&lsquo;rsatadiki,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">mamlakatda ishchi kuchi sifatini oshirishga qaratilgan</strong> siyosat olib borish talab etiladi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Yuqori malakali kadrlarni shakllantirishga</strong> alohida e&rsquo;tibor qaratish lozim.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bugungi kunda davlat muassasalarida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining 55 foiz</strong>dan ortig&lsquo;i ish qidiruvchilardan oliy ma&rsquo;lumot talab etmoqda. Xususiy sektorda esa asosiy talab -&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ish tajribasi</strong>. Masalan, yirik korxonalardagi bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">60% dan ortig&lsquo;i oliy ma&rsquo;lumotni talab qiladi</strong>, kichik korxonalarda esa atigi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5%</strong>. Bugungi kunda mehnat bozoriga ilk bor kirib kelayotgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">yoshlarning bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i 18 foizi</strong> oliy ma&rsquo;lumotga ega xolos.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shunday qilib, etalon mamlakatlar darajasiga erishish uchun yaqin kelajakda O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozori uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">muhandislar, texnologlar (oliy va o&lsquo;rta maxsus ta&rsquo;limga ega), dasturchilar, arxitektorlar, quruvchilar, menejerlar hamda yuqori malakali shifokor va o&lsquo;qituvchilar talab etiladi.</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTIning Inson kapitalini rivojlantirish va</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ijtimoiy tabaqalashuv masalalari bo&lsquo;yicha loyihasi</strong></h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;"><i class="bi bi-eye"></i> 3549</span></div></div></div></header></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><br></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div>
